    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been a reliable daily driver. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. Inside, the leather seats are well-preserved with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronics and mechanical systems are functioning properly, and it has a documented service history. It\u2019s a solid, well-cared-for car that offers great performance without the premium of a showroom-perfect model.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
