      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, heavy paint oxidation, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the interior requires a complete overhaul; the leather is cracked and torn, and the headliner is sagging. Mechanically, the car needs immediate attention as it has a persistent engine knock, a leaking cooling system, and the transmission shifts roughly. This would be an ideal candidate for a full restoration or a donor vehicle for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
