    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or parking lot imperfections, complemented by wheels that have never seen a curb. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and every digital interface operates with factory-new precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment. It comes complete with a meticulous service dossier, all original keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 48950.0,
